<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>C</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.  C     G           Am      F
 Maral móldir sýdy qalaı ańsasa,
.Dm      G7    C
 Meniń janym da,
.  C      G        Am    F
 Seni izdep shólirkeıdi, Táńir,
. Dm7  G7 C
 Seni ańsaıdy.

[C1]
.    Am           F    C
   Qudaıym, Sen qorǵanyshym,
.  F                  Dm        E
   Bar úmitim meniń, jigerim, kúshim,
.   C   G       Am   F
   Janymdy da, ómirimdi de,
.     Dm7   G  C
   Ózińe tek arnadym.

[V2]
 Kúndiz-túni raqym jasaǵan,
 Táńirimdi jyrlaımyn.
 Ómir bergen Qudaı Ákeme,
 Duǵamdy baǵyshtaımyn.

[C2]
   Baǵýshym, eń jaqyn Dosym,
   Jeteleıdi kúshti qolyń.
   Meıirimdi Táńir Iemdi,
   Ánimmen madaqtaımyn.</lyrics>
<title>Maral móldir sýdy qalaı ańsasa РӘЖ70</title>
